<small><i>Megachile manumuskin </i>Viereck, 1902; <i>Megachile &#40;Delomegachile&#41; addenda </i>Cresson, 1878; <i>Megachile &#40;Xanthosarus&#41; addenda </i>Cresson, 1878</small><p>
